           move      rf-fir-num-prt       to   w-out-fir-num-prt      .
           move      rf-fir-num-prg       to   w-out-fir-num-prg      .
           move      rf-fir-alf-pro       to   w-out-fir-alf-pro      .
           move      w-det-prg-fir-rgd
                    (w-det-prg-fir-ctr)   to   w-out-fir-des-pro      .
           move      rf-fir-qta-ven       to   w-out-fir-qta-fat      .
