           move      w-all-str-alf        to   w-out-fir-prz-net      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Prezzo netto standard                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Conversione in valuta base          *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
