           move      rf-fir-prz-nts       to   w-cvs-vlt-aav          .
           perform   cvs-alt-vlb-000      thru cvs-alt-vlb-999        .
           move      w-cvs-vlt-avb        to   rf-fir-prz-nts         .
       exe-exp-fir-dew-514.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
